highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Ahmedabad. Jhoome Jo Pathaan is the highest at #3.
Unholy (feat. Kim Petras) by Sam Smith and Kim Petras is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ahmedabad, up 28 spots at #32.
Tere Pyaar Mein by Pritam, Arijit Singh, Amitabh Bhattacharya, and Nikhita Gandhi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ahmedabad at #19.
Maan Meri Jaan by King has been on Top Songs Ahmedabad the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
